# Tone & Vertical Fit

Most "AI-generated" web design failures are not guardrail failures (wrong padding, missing focus state). They are **register failures**: the right design system applied to the wrong business. A pet shop styled like Linear is just as broken as a pet shop styled like Lorem-ipsum bootstrap mush — the user feels the wrongness, even if every spacing token is correct.

This rule exists to stop the model from defaulting to its training-data center of mass (dark mode, monochrome, Inter, dashboard funnel) for every brief.

---

## 1. Read the brief, classify the vertical

Before generating anything, classify the project into ONE row of the matrix below. If the brief is ambiguous, ask the user — do not assume "SaaS".

**Keyword triggers in the product name almost always determine the vertical:**

| Keyword in brief | Vertical |
|---|---|
| `shop`, `store`, `boutique`, `market`, `co.` | retail |
| `cafe`, `coffee`, `bakery`, `kitchen`, `restaurant`, `bar`, `bistro`, `eatery` | hospitality / food |
| `clinic`, `dental`, `vet`, `wellness`, `therapy`, `medspa`, `chiro` | health / wellness |
| `salon`, `barber`, `spa`, `nails`, `studio` (yoga/pilates/dance) | wellness / hospitality |
| `agency`, `studio` (design/dev), `lab`, `creative`, `co.` | agency / portfolio |
| `gym`, `fitness`, `crossfit`, `pilates`, `yoga` | fitness |
| `realty`, `homes`, `properties`, `estate` | real estate |
| `school`, `academy`, `learn`, `kids`, `tutor` | education / kids |
| `bank`, `pay`, `wallet`, `invest`, `loan`, `credit`, `card` | fintech |
| `cloud`, `infra`, `deploy`, `CI`, `db`, `api`, `dev`, `code`, `git` | dev tools |
| `analytics`, `dashboard`, `metrics`, `intel`, `ops` | b2b SaaS / analytics |
| `chat`, `mail`, `notes`, `tasks`, `calendar`, `social` | consumer SaaS |

If the keyword is `pet`, `dog`, `cat`, `bird`, `fish`: the vertical is determined by the noun next to it. `Pet Shop` → retail. `Pet Care App` → consumer SaaS. `Pet Clinic` → health.

---

## 2. Vertical → Aesthetic Matrix

| Vertical | Default mode | Reference systems | Hero imagery | Color register | Typography | Distinguishing trait |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Dev tools / DevOps / Infra** | dark (or system) | Vercel Geist, Linear, shadcn/ui | abstract, terminal, code, diagram | mono + 1 cool accent (blue/violet/green) | Geist / Inter / JetBrains Mono | restraint, monospace numerics |
| **Fintech (B2B)** | light or dark | Vercel Geist, Stripe, Linear | abstract diagrams, charts | mono + green or blue | Inter, Söhne | precise, trust-coded, lots of whitespace |
| **B2B SaaS / Analytics** | light by default | Linear, shadcn/ui, Stripe | dashboard screenshot, abstract | mono + 1 brand accent | Inter | data-rich hero, 3-up feature grid |
| **Consumer SaaS / productivity app** | light or dark | Apple HIG, Linear, shadcn/ui | actual app screenshot, friendly | brand-led, often 2 accents | Inter, SF Pro | screenshot of the real app, not a mockup |
| **Retail / E-commerce / Pet shop** | **light, warm** | Apple HIG, Shopify, Squarespace | **real product / lifestyle photo (REQUIRED)** | brand color + warm neutrals (cream, sand, off-white) | serif + sans (Playfair / DM Serif + Inter), or warm sans (Söhne, Recoleta) | photo dominates, products are the hero |
| **Restaurant / Cafe / Bar** | **light, warm** OR **dark moody** | Squarespace, custom editorial | **full-bleed food/place photo (REQUIRED)** | earthy (terracotta, olive, cream) OR moody (charcoal, gold, deep red) | serif display (Playfair, GT Sectra) + clean sans body | menu is the second-most-important thing after the photo |
| **Health / Wellness / Clinic** | **light, soft** | Apple HIG, Material 3 | calm photo (sky, hands, plants) or soft illustration | sage, cream, dusty blue, blush | rounded sans (Nunito, DM Sans) or warm serif | breathing room, no urgency, trust-coded |
| **Salon / Spa / Yoga** | **light, soft** OR muted dark | custom editorial | atmospheric portrait or place photo | beige, taupe, blush, sage | elegant serif + light sans | luxurious whitespace, sparse type |
| **Fitness / Gym / Crossfit** | **dark, high-contrast** | custom | **action photo (REQUIRED)** | mono + 1 saturated accent (orange/red/lime) | bold condensed sans (Bebas, Druk) | strong type, athletic energy |
| **Agency / Portfolio / Studio** | **light or extreme dark** | custom editorial | **case-study image or bold typography hero** | mono + 1 unexpected accent | typography-led — display serif or grotesque | hero is the work itself; chrome disappears |
| **Real Estate / Property** | light, calm | custom | **property photo (REQUIRED)** | warm neutrals + brand accent | serif display + sans | property cards with photo above all |
| **Education / Tutor / School** | light, friendly | Material 3, custom | photo of students or learning environment | brand + 1 supporting | rounded sans | clear hierarchy, accessible |
| **Children / Kids products** | light, playful, colorful | Material 3 expressive, custom | illustration + photo | bright multi-color, never grayscale | rounded sans (Quicksand, Rubik) | warmth, motion, friendliness |
| **Luxury / High-end / Fashion** | light or stark dark | custom editorial | **full-bleed editorial photo (REQUIRED)** | mono + gold OR pure mono | serif (Didot, GT Super) | extreme whitespace, sparse type, hero is the only thing |

